      <p>
        When you are adding venues or bands into the database, fields on your form may autofill with data from various sources.
        Our hope is that this will make it really easy for you to contribute.
        If there are venues you know or bands you love that aren't already listed, please add them, and feel free to upvote them
        to show support. We want to share information that will help us have better shows and better experiences booking tours.
      </p>
